{"tid":1776422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"OPPA全員退賽 竟然是這個原因！？（PD101JP）（驚嚇）","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T23:33:02.000Z","uid":149371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"482ada91c275b7f3dbee3c64462f4cb6a1371888","tid":1776422,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"日版Produce101再退賽兩人 <br />\n<br />\n韓國選手已全部退賽<br />\n<br />\n據日版Produce101官網公告，將辭退金潤東、鄭永勳兩位韓國選手。運營事務所表示在與他們商議後，尊重他們的意向同意退賽。繼上周另一名韓國選手金熙天退賽後，隊內的韓國選手已全部退賽。<br />\n<br />\n以下為官方網站的公告譯文：<br />\n<br />\n金潤東、鄭永勳辭退通知<br />\n<br />\n全民製作人的大家：<br />\n<br />\n我們接到了練習生金潤東、鄭永勳的辭退申請，經過與他們的多次商量後，運營事務所決定尊重本人的意見，接受了兩人的辭退申請，特此告知。<br />\n<br />\n在收錄第3回排名發表後大家也有異議，本日（12/5）的節目將按原內容照常播出。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我們在各社交平臺上發現部分實名者發佈無根據的誹謗中傷資訊。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓大家愉快地享受Product101這個項目，希望大家能夠理解並配合社交平臺的禮儀。<br />\n<br />\n今後也請繼續對PRODUCE 101 JAPAN、練習生多多支持關照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.sina.com.cn/y/yrihan/2019-12-05/doc-iihnzhfz3831544.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.sina.com.cn%2Fy%2Fyrihan%2F2019-12-05%2Fdoc-iihnzhfz3831544.shtml&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=27ffbfa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.sina.com.cn/y/yrihan/2019-12-05/doc-iihnzhfz3831544.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n潤東OPPA (;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ`) 😭 TT 😢 （咸了）<br />\n<br />\n我會不離不棄Gchi您的💘✊🏼<br />\n<br />\n😭💘✊🏼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QN8zyZr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQN8zyZr.jpg&h=a52cbaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/09/214932_f1b848e942733800c5aa664ae1646b20.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F09%2F214932_f1b848e942733800c5aa664ae1646b20.jpeg&h=0bbe6116&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/09/214933_91636d98c3f23c82ed4ffa0890bf397f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F09%2F214933_91636d98c3f23c82ed4ffa0890bf397f.jpeg&h=1352d6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOzyZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOzyZC.jpg&h=38e0f97c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"371256780faf4cb4a74b57ec598d5044f9f8926e","tid":1776422,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ`)"},{"pid":"8f0552c158b650b8d9804309793624a1c694933d","tid":1776422,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ`)"},{"pid":"32dde95140a43792f24070e35a95cc0b808eb855","tid":1776422,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ`)"},{"pid":"12f17a0f52eff201ff1eda653d133132fe296a1c","tid":1776422,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b90de04ee6308ebb7030b4b2ed4766ad8cbf0f0d","tid":1776422,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f17a0f52eff201ff1eda653d133132fe296a1c","tid":1776422,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:56.000Z",